articles.headline: Jonathan Kraft says Chandler Jones 'handled this appropriately'
articles.description: Jonathan Kraft talked publicly for the first time on Chandler Jones being admitted to a hospital after reportedly having a bad reaction to synthetic marijuana.

articles.headline: Part of Ted Marchibroda's legacy was defining the mantra 'Play like a Raven'
articles.description: Ted Marchibroda, who died Saturday at 84, helped build the foundation of Ravens football -- play with passion and keep fighting.

articles.headline: Chiefs' Jeremy Maclin, Pats' Rob Gronkowski both active
articles.description: The Chiefs' Jeremy Maclin and the Patriots' Rob Gronkowski are both active for Saturday's AFC divisional round playoff game.

images.name: Chiefs, Patriots prepared for bad weather in New England
images.caption: Bob Holtzman reports from Gillette Stadium in Foxborough, Mass., where the Chiefs and Patriots will meet in an AFC divisional playoff matchup.

articles.headline: Ted Marchibroda dies at age 84
articles.description: Ted Marchibroda, who spent 12 seasons as the coach of the Colts and Ravens and played in the NFL for four years, has died at age 84.

images.name: Ted Marchibroda [600x400]
images.caption: Ted Marchibroda coached the Colts in two stints, once in Baltimore in the 1970s and then in Indianapolis in the 1990s.

articles.headline: Edelman's 'disappointed Tom Brady' impression
articles.description: Patriots WR Julian Edelman shares his best impression of Tom Brady when Brady is disappointed in him.

images.name: Edelman's 'disappointed Tom Brady' impression
images.caption: Patriots WR Julian Edelman shares his best impression of Tom Brady when Brady is disappointed in him.

articles.headline: Edelman recalls moving to L.A. to be near Tom Brady
articles.description: Once a gopher for Tom Brady, Julian Edelman explains that he moved to Los Angeles to be near Brady and eventually started to get invited over to Tom's house for lunch.
